```

### 38.3 模块职责
- `bins/api`：启?HTTP 服务，组?Router ?AppState?- `bins/worker`：启动异步任务执行器?- `transport-http`：REST、SSE、中间件、错误映射?- `rag-core`：Planner、Runtime、retrievers、rerank、merge、context assembly?- `ingestion`：解析、分块、摘要、embedding、索引写入编排?- `storage-pg`：事务、RLS、回表、审计?- `storage-qdrant`：向量写入、payload filter、Dense 检紃69?- `cache-redis`：缓存、限流、锁、幂等键?- `llm`：Planner、生成、重排模型适配?- `telemetry`：metrics、trace、structured log?- `test-kit`：fixture、容器、黄金集?
### 38.4 依赖规则
- `transport-http -> app -> rag-core / ingestion / auth / billing ...`
- `rag-core -> storage-pg / storage-qdrant / llm / cache-redis / telemetry / common`
- `ingestion -> storage-pg / storage-qdrant / llm / cache-redis / telemetry / common`
- 外围模块不得反向依赖 `transport-http`?
